A*x² + B*y² + C*z² = 0
x = x0 + t1
y = y0 + t2
z = z0 + t3

A(x0 + t * a)^2 + B(y0 + t * b)^2 + C(z0 + t * c)^2 = 0

A(x0² + 2ta +  t²a²) +
B(y0² + 2tb +  t²b²) +
C(z0² + 2tc +  t²c²)

Aa² t² + 2aA t + x0²A +
Bb² t² + 2bB t + y0²B +
Cc² t² + 2cC t + z0²C

t² * (Aa² + Bb² + Cc²) + t(2(aA + bB + cC) + x0²A + y0²B + z0²C = 

normal:
2*A*x
2*B*y
2*C*z